{#- swing/web/templates/partials/hypothesis_recommendations.html.j2 -#}
{#- Frontend brief §4.2 — top-N hypothesis-driven recommendations. The
    surrounding {% if %} guard means the section vanishes entirely when
    `vm.active_recommendations` is empty (empty tuple → falsy in Jinja).
    Kept as a partial so future routes (watchlist, dedicated page) can
    include the same markup without copy/paste drift.

    Task 5.4 — chevron column added as the leading column; per-row markup
    extracted to `partials/hypothesis_recommendations_row.html.j2` so the
    refresh route, full-page render, and post-close swap-back all flow
    through the same single source of truth (CLAUDE.md HTMX OOB-swap drift
    gotcha).

    Task 4 (hyp-recs success-path fix) — `oob` flag:
    - oob=False (default, legacy behavior): the section element is emitted
      ONLY when `vm.active_recommendations` is non-empty.
    - oob=True: the section element is ALWAYS emitted (even when recs are
      empty) and carries `hx-swap-oob="true"`. Required by entry_post's
      success-path response so HTMX has a valid OOB-swap target on
      `#hypothesis-recommendations` even when the operator just traded
      their only remaining hyp-rec. The empty-OOB branch drops the
      `hypothesis-recommendations` class (so no chrome bleeds through CSS)
      and adds the HTML5 `hidden` global attribute. The populated branch
      keeps the class so a subsequent OOB swap to a populated section
      restores full styling.

    Single source of truth — CLAUDE.md "HTMX OOB-swap partial drift" gotcha
    forbids hand-duplicating this markup at any callsite. -#}
{%- set oob = oob|default(false) -%}
{% if vm.active_recommendations %}
<section id="hypothesis-recommendations" class="hypothesis-recommendations"{% if oob %} hx-swap-oob="true"{% endif %}>
  <h2>Hypothesis-driven recommendations</h2>
  <table class="hypothesis-recommendations">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th aria-label="Expand"></th>
        <th>Chart</th>
        <th>Ticker</th>
        <th>Price</th>
        <th>Pivot</th>
        <th>Hypothesis</th>
        <th>Progress</th>
        <th>Tripwire</th>
        <th>Suggested label</th>
        <th aria-label="Action"></th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      {% for rec in vm.active_recommendations %}
        {% include "partials/hypothesis_recommendations_row.html.j2" %}
      {% endfor %}
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>
{% elif oob %}
<section id="hypothesis-recommendations" hx-swap-oob="true" hidden></section>
{% endif %}
